{"tid":2510262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁凱晴六四集會未經批准集結罪成即時還押 與岑敖暉黃之鋒袁嘉蔚同於下星期四判刑","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T05:02:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7f1ac3ea813d56b0140e6616911cece482894e","tid":2510262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"觀塘願景 - 梁凱晴 Jannelle R. Leung:<br />\n<br />\n四名被告全部即時還押，下星期四判刑<br />\nBy 願景小編<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kwuntongfuture/posts/767324647485657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkwuntongfuture%2Fposts%2F767324647485657&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=bca88d40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwuntongfuture/posts/767324647485657</a>"},{"pid":"4a650de6575626ca3195779dfd31b5adf5b23feb","tid":2510262,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670545227d456e7f8ef5ab0dab393c0bbb3a3d75","tid":2510262,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1022ff23da2441d48e6fbe8c4877b22ad7711ed1","tid":2510262,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d3f675b0a5cdf0fecf13db11d42ad363ac077","tid":2510262,"uid":274921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0238329198a3d73761d35222c344e4de959629","tid":2510262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"支聯會去年6月4日申請在維園舉辦六四31周年燭光晚會，但史無前例遭警方禁止，當晚市民自發進入維園悼念。24人遭票控「明知而參與未經批准集結」、「煽惑未經批准集結」及「舉行一個未經批准集結」罪，其中前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、南區區議員袁嘉蔚、荃灣區議員岑敖暉和觀塘區議員梁凱晴今日（30日）於區域法院承認「明知而參與未經批准集結」罪。法官陳廣池聽過4人的求情後，押後判刑至5月6日，並下令4人還柙。<br />\n<br />\n眾人聽聞被告須還柙後，隨即錯愕道：「吓？」4人之中唯一仍是自由身的梁凱晴，被懲教人員帶離時，立即高舉三隻手指的手勢。黃之鋒大叫：「就算改變唔到世界，都唔好俾世界改變自己！」岑敖暉則向太太余思朗展示「韓式心心」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊以英語進行。甫開庭，律師表示4名被告均不需要傳譯員，惟法官陳廣池指，基於4人的身份，認為仍然有需要將聆訊內容翻譯成中文，讓庭內聽審人士能夠明白。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年4月23日，蔡耀昌代表支聯會向警方申請在維園舉辦「悼念六四31年」集會，預計出席人數有5至10萬。惟警方參考衛生署建議，指新冠肺炎是高度傳染性，疫情期間不適宜進行群眾聚集，否則對市民構成風險；即使保持1.5米社交距離和8人一組，也不可行。<br />\n<br />\n六四當晚，警方在維園外設立多個揚聲器廣播，呼籲市民不要參與群眾聚集，康文署亦關閉了足球場。晚上約6時36分，李卓人帶領約100人由噴水池公園進入維園足球場，公眾人士和記者緊隨其後。之後有人推倒圍著足球場的鐵馬，約7時04分，李卓人與約400人逗留在6號足球場，其後愈來愈多人到場聚集。他們大部份身穿黑衣、手持蠟燭。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上7時09分至8時，黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚及梁凱晴在6號球場坐下，他們身穿黑色衣服、手持蠟燭及白色花束。黃之鋒兩度接受傳媒訪問，李卓人亦一度走近4人小談。之後李卓人叫喊與平反六四有關的口號，群眾亦有回應。李又播放六四相關影片、帶領群眾唱歌、焚燒弔唁冊，至8時43分宣告集會結束。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒正就包圍警總案服刑，袁嘉蔚及岑敖暉因初選案而還柙，是次聆訊可謂久違的露面機會。開庭前，岑敖暉不斷與旁聽席朋友打招呼、舉起姆指，又與剛出獄的林朗彥比對「手瓜」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%834%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E6%99%B4%E9%A6%96%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E4%BF%BE%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%259C%25834%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%2599%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%2599-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=6c97f72a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%259C%25834%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%2599%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%2599-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1&h=8c2e79ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%834%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A2%81%E5%87%B1%E6%99%B4%E9%A6%96%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E4%BF%BE%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1</a>"}]}